            %\item Beverton\&Holt stock-recruitment model
            %\item model selection using Akaike Information Criteria (AIC)
        %\end{itemize}
      \end{block}

      \begin{block}{Monte Carlo}

        The method was tested with Monte Carlo simulations to assess if it allowed to estimate natural mortality.
        
